  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nuse **nohup** to run lighthouse background, but lighthouse random shut down and print log as below\r\n\r\n> Sep 12 13:20:07.620 INFO Shutting down..                         reason: Success(\"Received SIGHUP\")\r\n> Sep 12 13:20:07.633 INFO Saved DHT state                         service: network\r\n> Sep 12 13:20:07.633 INFO Network service shutdown                service: network\r\n> Sep 12 13:20:09.418 INFO Saved beacon chain to disk              service: beacon\r\n> Sep 12 13:20:09.643 WARN Unable to free worker                   error: channel closed, msg: did not free worker, shutdown may be underway\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nLighthouse v3.1.0-aa022f4\r\nBLS library: blst-portable\r\nSHA256 hardware acceleration: false\r\nSpecs: mainnet (true), minimal (false), gnosis (true)\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nDescribe the present behaviour of the application, with regards to this\r\nissue.\r\n\r\nlighthouse random shut down.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nlighthouse should be work always\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nrun command\r\n\r\n`\r\nnohup lighthouse --network goerli beacon_node --http --execution-endpoint http://localhost:8551 --execution-jwt ~/ethereum/consensus/prysm/jwt.hex --checkpoint-sync-url https://<projectId>:<secrete key>@eth2-beacon-prater.infura.io --purge-db &\r\n`\r\n",
