    "body": "I think `nohup` does not work because lighthouse does implement its own `SIGHUP` [handler](https://sourcegraph.com/github.com/sigp/lighthouse/-/blob/lighthouse/environment/src/lib.rs?L410:37). I think `nohup lighthouse ...  & disown` at least prevent lighthouse from stopping when you exit the shell.",
